    "name": "Hogtie",
    "steam_appid": 3054330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br>Hogtie带你踏上获奖之旅，化身为西部荒野的英雄泰德，他的可靠套索是成功的关键。这款仓库番（Sokoban）解谜游戏挑战你像真正的牧牛人一样思考，每个关卡都要求你在不同的生物群系中围捕逃跑的小猪。<br><br><strong>[h2玩法机制:[/h2]</strong><br><strong>禁止推拉</strong><br>这些小猪不能被推拉——你需要用套索把它们拖走，为经典的仓库番解谜机制带来了新的变化。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/5231704cf4cafd335b1d0dbee1301c69.poster.avif?t=1752151516\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/5231704cf4cafd335b1d0dbee1301c69.webm?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/5231704cf4cafd335b1d0dbee1301c69.mp4?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>套索</strong><br>你的套索将成为你的生命线。你将用它将逃跑的小猪拖回猪圈，穿越险恶的环境。每个关卡都会用各种机制来考验你的套索技能，从躲避致命障碍到策略性地绕过环境危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/126bc5a4106bdf986a2fd6f55d634c2d.poster.avif?t=1752151516\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/126bc5a4106bdf986a2fd6f55d634c2d.webm?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/126bc5a4106bdf986a2fd6f55d634c2d.mp4?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>每一步都很重要</strong><br>根据你的行动效率，每个关卡最多可以获得三颗星。无论你是打算以最高效率解谜还是更喜欢轻松的方式，你可以根据自己的游戏风格来选择挑战的难度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/022ec95c63bd7936230127e79f1ee420.poster.avif?t=1752151516\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/022ec95c63bd7936230127e79f1ee420.webm?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/022ec95c63bd7936230127e79f1ee420.mp4?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义</h2></strong><br>喜欢农场风格还是一点西部荒野的魅力？或者是一套华丽的西装，还是全身皮革装扮？别担心，在Hogtie中，你可以根据自己的个性和风格自定义泰德和他忠实的坐骑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/57a41d82ee51f7fb2124b39312b0ebf9.poster.avif?t=1752151516\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/57a41d82ee51f7fb2124b39312b0ebf9.webm?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054330/extras/57a41d82ee51f7fb2124b39312b0ebf9.mp4?t=1752151516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>掸去你的靴子上的灰尘，拿起你的套索，准备应对西部最疯狂的谜题。你准备好捆绑一些小猪了吗？",
